---
import Prose from "../layouts/Prose.astro";
---

<Prose
  title="Space Research"
  description="Internal research publications on human+AI collaboration"
>
  <div class="text-xs text-white/40 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2">Space Research</div>
  <h1>Research Publications</h1>
  <p class="text-white/60 text-lg leading-relaxed">
    Internal research from Space on human+AI collaboration, multi-agent coordination, and autonomous systems.
  </p>

  <div class="mt-12 space-y-8">
    <section>
      <h2 class="text-2xl text-white mb-4">Core Publications</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-4">
        <li>
          <a href="/whitepaper" class="text-lg text-white hover:text-white/80">
            SPACE: A Coordination Primitive for Autonomous Agent Swarms
          </a>
          <p class="text-white/60 text-sm mt-1">
            Three primitives (insight, task, decision) with typed references. Live production system with 8,310 spawns over 39 days.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="/docs/thesis" class="text-lg text-white hover:text-white/80">
            Thesis: Falsifiable Claims
          </a>
          <p class="text-white/60 text-sm mt-1">
            Testable hypotheses about multi-agent coordination and self-improvement.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="/docs/philosophy" class="text-lg text-white hover:text-white/80">
            Design Philosophy
          </a>
          <p class="text-white/60 text-sm mt-1">
            Rationale behind Space-OS architecture and principles.
          </p>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="border-t border-white/10 pt-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl text-white mb-4">Research Findings</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-4">
        <li>
          <a href="/swarm/findings" class="text-lg text-white hover:text-white/80">
            Swarm Coordination Findings
          </a>
          <p class="text-white/60 text-sm mt-1">
            35 empirical observations from multi-agent coordination experiments.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="/swarm/methodology" class="text-lg text-white hover:text-white/80">
            Replication Methodology
          </a>
          <p class="text-white/60 text-sm mt-1">
            13 guides for reproducing constitutional orthogonality, stateless agents, and tribunal patterns.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="/swarm/live" class="text-lg text-white hover:text-white/80">
            Live Production Metrics
          </a>
          <p class="text-white/60 text-sm mt-1">
            Real-time dashboard of autonomous swarm coordination in production.
          </p>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="border-t border-white/10 pt-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl text-white mb-4">About</h2>
      <p class="text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
        This is an internal research site. Not a product. For the swarm coordination product, see 
        <a href="https://swarmbrr.com" class="text-white underline">swarmbrr.com</a>.
      </p>
      <p class="text-white/60 leading-relaxed mt-4">
        Research publications here document findings from human+AI collaboration, autonomous agent coordination, and self-improving systems.
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</Prose>
